[
    {
        "text": "People have been curious about this for a while so you go back,...",
        "startTime": 4583,
        "endTime": 7857,
        "slowStartTime": 7024,
        "slowEndTime": 12010
    },
    {
        "text": "...and here's a beautiful example, to the 1920s.",
        "startTime": 7958,
        "endTime": 10748,
        "slowStartTime": 12087,
        "slowEndTime": 16347
    },
    {
        "text": "A young scientist by the name of Asa Schaeffer asked a friend,...",
        "startTime": 10968,
        "endTime": 14184,
        "slowStartTime": 16602,
        "slowEndTime": 21501
    },
    {
        "text": " ...\"Could you put on a blindfold?\"",
        "startTime": 14745,
        "endTime": 16133,
        "slowStartTime": 22268,
        "slowEndTime": 24425
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I'm going to take you to the edge of a field.\"",
        "startTime": 16267,
        "endTime": 17913,
        "slowStartTime": 24550,
        "slowEndTime": 27094
    },
    {
        "text": "And he said, \"What I'd like you to do is walk across this field in a straight line.\"",
        "startTime": 17977,
        "endTime": 22811,
        "slowStartTime": 27115,
        "slowEndTime": 34442
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Just stay as straight on course as you possibly can.\"",
        "startTime": 22906,
        "endTime": 26130,
        "slowStartTime": 34509,
        "slowEndTime": 39420
    },
    {
        "text": "So the man headed off and here is Asa's map of what happened next.",
        "startTime": 26339,
        "endTime": 31721,
        "slowStartTime": 39658,
        "slowEndTime": 47807
    },
    {
        "text": "The man starts to walk and his route as you see here...",
        "startTime": 31799,
        "endTime": 34930,
        "slowStartTime": 47849,
        "slowEndTime": 52620
    },
    {
        "text": "...begins to tilt ever so slightly to the right.",
        "startTime": 35063,
        "endTime": 37838,
        "slowStartTime": 52744,
        "slowEndTime": 56982
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm gonna speed this up just a bit.",
        "startTime": 38281,
        "endTime": 39612,
        "slowStartTime": 57571,
        "slowEndTime": 59643
    },
    {
        "text": "Notice that the blindfolded man now starts to turn dramatically,...",
        "startTime": 39725,
        "endTime": 43965,
        "slowStartTime": 59738,
        "slowEndTime": 66172
    },
    {
        "text": "...taking him back to the road where he started from,...",
        "startTime": 44067,
        "endTime": 46681,
        "slowStartTime": 66250,
        "slowEndTime": 70247
    },
    {
        "text": "...and then across the road and then around again and then back again and around again.",
        "startTime": 46751,
        "endTime": 52245,
        "slowStartTime": 70277,
        "slowEndTime": 78593
    },
    {
        "text": "And increasingly he's moving in smaller curls until finally he hits a tree and stops.",
        "startTime": 52313,
        "endTime": 58333,
        "slowStartTime": 78619,
        "slowEndTime": 87725
    },
    {
        "text": "All the while he thought he was walking in a perfectly straight line.",
        "startTime": 58952,
        "endTime": 62784,
        "slowStartTime": 88578,
        "slowEndTime": 94401
    },
    {
        "text": "Strange?",
        "startTime": 62958,
        "endTime": 63447,
        "slowStartTime": 94587,
        "slowEndTime": 95395
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, there are many studies just like this.",
        "startTime": 63571,
        "endTime": 66275,
        "slowStartTime": 95506,
        "slowEndTime": 99638
    },
    {
        "text": "From 1928, here are three people who leave a barn on a very foggy day...",
        "startTime": 66915,
        "endTime": 71913,
        "slowStartTime": 100522,
        "slowEndTime": 108094
    },
    {
        "text": "...and what they want to do is go to a point about a half mile away.",
        "startTime": 72008,
        "endTime": 75534,
        "slowStartTime": 108162,
        "slowEndTime": 113526
    },
    {
        "text": "Here's what happened, the map version.",
        "startTime": 76190,
        "endTime": 79037,
        "slowStartTime": 114435,
        "slowEndTime": 118781
    },
    {
        "text": "The barn is here.",
        "startTime": 79187,
        "endTime": 80280,
        "slowStartTime": 118931,
        "slowEndTime": 120645
    },
    {
        "text": "The destination is here.",
        "startTime": 81367,
        "endTime": 82769,
        "slowStartTime": 122201,
        "slowEndTime": 124379
    },
    {
        "text": "Now watch this, off they go.",
        "startTime": 83456,
        "endTime": 85282,
        "slowStartTime": 125334,
        "slowEndTime": 128148
    },
    {
        "text": "They think they're walking straight, but instead what they actually do is that they start to turn...",
        "startTime": 85833,
        "endTime": 90478,
        "slowStartTime": 128900,
        "slowEndTime": 135942
    },
    {
        "text": "...and turn and turn and end up, weirdly, back in the very place they started, the barn!",
        "startTime": 90973,
        "endTime": 98605,
        "slowStartTime": 136610,
        "slowEndTime": 148133
    },
    {
        "text": "This experiment has been done in all kinds of situations.",
        "startTime": 99625,
        "endTime": 102317,
        "slowStartTime": 149588,
        "slowEndTime": 153701
    },
    {
        "text": "Here's another 1928 study.",
        "startTime": 102374,
        "endTime": 104027,
        "slowStartTime": 153711,
        "slowEndTime": 156265
    },
    {
        "text": "A man is blindfolded and then asked to jump into a lake...",
        "startTime": 104485,
        "endTime": 107737,
        "slowStartTime": 156877,
        "slowEndTime": 161831
    },
    {
        "text": "...and swim in a straight line to the other side.",
        "startTime": 108668,
        "endTime": 111479,
        "slowStartTime": 163152,
        "slowEndTime": 167444
    },
    {
        "text": "And here is where he swam.",
        "startTime": 111559,
        "endTime": 114547,
        "slowStartTime": 167488,
        "slowEndTime": 172046
    },
    {
        "text": "There is apparently a profound inability in humans to stick to a straight line when blindfolded...",
        "startTime": 115152,
        "endTime": 121191,
        "slowStartTime": 172878,
        "slowEndTime": 182012
    },
    {
        "text": "...or when there is no fixed point, no sun, no moon, no mountaintop, to guide them.",
        "startTime": 121949,
        "endTime": 127893,
        "slowStartTime": 183073,
        "slowEndTime": 192065
    },
    {
        "text": "In this last case, a blindfolded man is asked to get into a car...",
        "startTime": 128455,
        "endTime": 132310,
        "slowStartTime": 192832,
        "slowEndTime": 198690
    },
    {
        "text": "...and is told to drive in a straight line across a totally empty Kansas field.",
        "startTime": 133111,
        "endTime": 139340,
        "slowStartTime": 199816,
        "slowEndTime": 209235
    },
    {
        "text": "Now the driver is not in any danger, all he has to do is hold course.",
        "startTime": 139488,
        "endTime": 143427,
        "slowStartTime": 209382,
        "slowEndTime": 215366
    },
    {
        "text": "But here is the map that shows what happened next.",
        "startTime": 143539,
        "endTime": 146044,
        "slowStartTime": 215459,
        "slowEndTime": 219291
    },
    {
        "text": "For 80 years, scientists have been trying to explain this tendency...",
        "startTime": 147135,
        "endTime": 151033,
        "slowStartTime": 220852,
        "slowEndTime": 226775
    },
    {
        "text": "...to turn when you think you're going straight.",
        "startTime": 151147,
        "endTime": 153394,
        "slowStartTime": 226870,
        "slowEndTime": 230316
    },
    {
        "text": "They thought maybe this is some form of handedness, like being a righty or a lefty.",
        "startTime": 153942,
        "endTime": 158576,
        "slowStartTime": 231063,
        "slowEndTime": 238089
    },
    {
        "text": "Or maybe it's a right-left brain thing,...",
        "startTime": 158631,
        "endTime": 160581,
        "slowStartTime": 238097,
        "slowEndTime": 241097
    },
    {
        "text": "...where one side of you is slightly dominant and then the dominance builds over time.",
        "startTime": 160646,
        "endTime": 165487,
        "slowStartTime": 241119,
        "slowEndTime": 248456
    },
    {
        "text": "Maybe it's just simple asymmetry.",
        "startTime": 165938,
        "endTime": 168191,
        "slowStartTime": 249057,
        "slowEndTime": 252511
    },
    {
        "text": "Some people are stronger on one side or have different-sized arms or legs...",
        "startTime": 168255,
        "endTime": 172702,
        "slowStartTime": 252532,
        "slowEndTime": 259278
    },
    {
        "text": "But try as they might, and we're still trying these experiments,...",
        "startTime": 172823,
        "endTime": 176904,
        "slowStartTime": 259385,
        "slowEndTime": 265581
    },
    {
        "text": "...nobody has really figured out why we can't go straight.",
        "startTime": 177193,
        "endTime": 181626,
        "slowStartTime": 265940,
        "slowEndTime": 272664
    }
]